        public void matchFlows​(String mobileFlowFile,
                       String wearFlowFile)
        Simple algorithm to calculate the connection between sources and sinks from a mobile-wearable app. If you need to calculate more than 1 connection for the same initial flow, don't use this function. use deepFlowAnalysis(org.json.simple.JSONObject,java.util.List<java.util.ArrayList<org.json.simple.JSONObject>>), instead
